    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 credibility factors. Seven factors were assessed and all fell below required levels. Six factors were not assessed and represent epistemic gaps at MRL 5. Despite these deficiencies, the package is formally accepted for submission to demonstrate compound risk escalation detection. The orphan claim (no prov:wasDerivedFrom) and the absence of uncertainty quantification across all validation results represent the primary evidence weaknesses triggering COMPOUND-01.",
